lead_paragraph: Substitute Divock Origi and James Milner both scored as Liverpool beat Sunderland 2-0 at Anfield to return provisionally to the Premier League summit on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Origi and Milner Give Liverpool 2-0 Win Over Sunderland
